307
00:14:58,160 --> 00:15:00,680
Distinguished leaders and teachers,
good afternoon.

308
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:02,560
I am Kang Yide from Binhai University.

309
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:04,040
I'm honored to invite you

310
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:06,120
