315
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:20,920
Where did you get plums?

316
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,560
From the wine.

317
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,360
Really tasty.

318
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,440
I saved one for you.

319
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:27,000
So, my wish is

320
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,480
