323
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,560
As the initiator and organizer

324
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,000
of the event,

325
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:39,160
I hope that all leaders and teachers

326
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,800
could give us your full support.

327
00:15:44,532 --> 00:15:45,360
(College Film Festival Seminar)

328
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:48,040
Next, let's invite

329
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:50,040
a participant from Binhai University

330
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:52,240
