331
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:52,920
Please.

332
00:15:59,059 --> 00:16:00,920
(Let the Youth Take the Stage)

333
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:03,240
Distinguished leaders and teachers,
good afternoon.

334
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,800
I am Li Yanhao from

335
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:06,480
the Library Management Department
of Binhai University.

336
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:07,920
Great!

337
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:17,560
I feel very honored to be here

338
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,120
to give you the report.

339
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,040
I'm very happy

340
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:23,360
to participate in our film festival.

341
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,040
Who is that?

342
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,000
How much wine did he drink?

343
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:31,560
Oh,

344
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:33,560
here,

345
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:36,600
I'd like to discuss in depth with you

346
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,560
