- Do something!

347
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:40,480
How? Teachers are all here.

348
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,480
A different kind of movie

349
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:43,040
- with innovative ideas.
- Come back!

350
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,480
- And then, as a college student,
- Come back!

351
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,360
I will also

352
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,920
work very hard to shoot my movie well

353
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:50,920
in the film festival.

354
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:53,160
By the way, we have

355
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,360
a very professional producer,

356
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:58,040
excellent makeup artists
and art department.

357
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,160
Right. There's also...

358
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:01,920
A good cameraman!

359
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,040
That's me!

360
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:04,120
Who is this?

361
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:05,720
Who is he?

362
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,560
I am the cameraman.

363
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:07,720
- He's drunk.
- Do you know him?

364
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,120
- Is he from our school?
- I don't know him.

365
00:17:09,120 --> 00:17:09,800
No.

366
00:17:10,080 --> 00:17:11,080
Look at what he is doing.

367
00:17:11,080 --> 00:17:12,200
What's he here for?

368
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,560
I don't know him, either.

369
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,440
Look.

370
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:16,920
Look at him.

371
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:20,360
Why did you come up? Go down!

372
00:17:20,360 --> 00:17:21,720
Go away.

373
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:24,080
Hello everyone, my name is Xiao Rang.

374
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:26,080
He is our cameraman.

375
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,600
Li Yanhao

376
00:17:28,040 --> 00:17:29,600
