377
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:30,600
Growing up,

378
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,320
we always have clear roles.

379
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:33,960
He is leading, and I'm supporting.

380
00:17:34,120 --> 00:17:35,360
He is flower and I am leaves.

381
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,360
He is Rukawa Kaede

382
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,600
and I am Sakuragi Hanamichi.

383
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:39,600
Although he is rather ordinary,

384
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,960
and self-righteous,

385
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:44,080
as long as he believes he can make films

386
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:44,920
and be a director,

387
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:47,120
I'll have his back as the cameraman.

388
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:49,240
Right, he is very professional.

389
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,920
Let's take a break.

390
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,800
You know why he wants to be a director?

391
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:54,360
Do something!

392
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,080
For love!

393
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:57,600
Love?

394
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:58,120
He and...

395
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,840
Shut up.

396
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:04,480
We are young.

397
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,360
We must be brave.

398
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:11,600
- What's going on?
- Look at the young people.

399
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,440
(Let the Youth Take the Stage)
Let's go.

400
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,960
Go.

401
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:15,960
Are you crazy?

402
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,320
I won't go.

403
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:19,080
Hurry up.

404
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,080
Come down.

405
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:28,200
Go.

406
00:18:46,995 --> 00:18:50,912
(University Student Film Festival
Seminar)

407
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,720
Didn't you promise

408
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,440
to help me with the film festival?

409
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:55,480
Yes, I did.

410
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,200
I am helping you now.

411
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:58,720
Think about it, without me,

412
00:18:58,720 --> 00:19:00,320
could the film festival be so great?

413
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:01,320
But why didn't you

414
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:02,960
tell me that you decided to extend it

415
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,680
to all schools in the city?

416
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,960
It was a last-minute idea.

417
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:08,080
Since we are going to do it,

418
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:09,720
we should make it big, right?

419
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,600
I've done so much before.

420
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,960
I know you've done a lot

421
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,320
and made a lot of efforts.

422
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:15,600
But these are not enough.

423
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:19,320
Introducing someone like Li Yanhao

424
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,600
is not enough to make an impact.

425
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:23,960
Today he is...

426
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:24,720
Yu Lan.

427
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:27,440
You need to improve your abilities.

428
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:30,080
I've organized such a large meeting

429
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:30,840
with so many guests

430
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,440
attending our film Festival.

431
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,840
Li Yanhao and his friends

432
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:35,840
disrupted the event today,

433
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,320
but it doesn't matter.

434
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:38,600
Because of me,

435
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:40,320
leaders won't make a big deal of it.

436
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,320
- But I...
- Yu Lan.

437
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:45,840
Think it over.

438
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,440
A Film Festival organized
by a single school

439
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:50,080
and a city-wide one,

440
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,080
isn't it obvious

441
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:52,440
the latter has bigger influence?

442
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,840
For such a big event,

443
00:19:55,600 --> 00:19:58,120
your abilities are not enough.

444
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:00,960
So I must be the top organizer.

445
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:05,720
I know you've made a lot of efforts

446
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,320
and gained a lot of experience.

447
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,200
So,

448
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:10,320
after it ends,
I'll issue you a certificate

449
00:20:10,560 --> 00:20:12,200
in the name of the main organizer.

450
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:14,240
As a recognition of your work.

451
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,600
I don't want any certificates.

452
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,960
I just want to do it well

453
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,720
from the start to the end.

454
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,840
Now, I am helping you

455
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,320
to do this thing better.

456
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,720
To get more students involved

457
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:23,720
and expand our influence.

458
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:24,840
That's not what I want.

459
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:26,200
But this is what I want.

460
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,200
I've talked with the teacher.

461
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:38,200
It's decided.

462
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:41,440
From now on, I'll handle all matters

463
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:43,240
regarding the Film Festival.

464
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:47,720
If you're still willing to work with me,

465
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:49,840
join me.

466
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,240
If not,

467
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,600
go and enjoy your summer vacation.

468
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:28,440
Awake now?

469
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:33,320
Why am I here?

470
00:21:33,320 --> 00:21:34,960
Remember what you did this afternoon?

471
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:37,080
What did I do?

472
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,440
Shame on you.

473
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:39,480
You got drunk

474
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,080
and disrupted the seminar.

475
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,840
We wheel you back on a cart.

476
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,480
Xu Xiangdong

477
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,960
forced me to eat those plums.

478
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,960
I was sober

479
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:55,600
until I ate the plums.

480
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,600
I don't know you can be so strong
when you got drunk.

481
00:21:58,600 --> 00:21:59,920
We couldn't hold you down.

482
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:07,840
I was careless.

483
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:22,040
I think

484
00:22:22,040 --> 00:22:24,320
leaving Li Jiatong to wash all dishes

485
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:25,600
isn't quite appropriate.

486
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:28,200
Then you go help her.

487
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:34,320
What's inappropriate about it?

488
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:36,200
We cook, and she washes dishes.

489
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:38,240
Isn't that fair?

490
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,600
It is.

491
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,960
But I think

492
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,600
you should take a look.

493
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:45,240
Take a look?

494
00:22:47,320 --> 00:22:48,720
Okay.

495
00:22:57,080 --> 00:22:58,200
Li Yanhao

496
00:22:58,200 --> 00:22:59,600
films to chase another girl,

497
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:00,720
leaving me washing dishes.

498
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:02,320
I'll make you pay.

499
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:04,840
Make you pay!

500
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:05,960
Who will pay?

501
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,440
One minute later,

502
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,440
it will be you.

503
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:13,840
So angry, huh?

504
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:15,440
They made me come to help you.

505
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:17,080
You've finished it all, haven't you?

506
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,320
They sent you to help me?

507
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,200
What about you?

508
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,600
I told them

509
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:22,960
you wouldn't need my help.

510
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:23,600
You can do it

511
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:25,600
perfectly and happily.

512
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:26,320
See?

513
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,200
I'm right.

514
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:29,560
Good job!

515
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:31,960
Good job?

516
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:33,840
Bye.

517
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:35,080
Li Yanhao!

518
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,120
See, you guys,

519
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,960
I listened to you and went to help,

520
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,080
but she didn't need it.

521
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,080
Alright, then I'll go for a walk.

522
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:51,440
Walk a long way after a meal,
and one could live long.

523
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,600
Live long?

524
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:54,320
When you come back, you're doomed!

525
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:04,840
Young man!

526
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:05,960
Come here!

527
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:08,080
(Natural coconut)
Buy a delicious coconut and try.

528
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:08,680
Alright?

529
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,440
How much is it?

530
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,320
Thirty yuan each.

531
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:14,600
That's expensive.

532
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,200
Not at all!

533
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:17,320
Let me tell you,

534
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,600
the people here

535
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,120
all do business honestly.

536
00:24:20,320 --> 00:24:21,960
No one scams customers.

537
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,440
Sure.

538
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:24,440
It's great.

539
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,720
Don't hesitate anymore.

540
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:28,320
Buy a coconut.

541
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,720
I'll tell you a story.

542
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:30,840
What story?

543
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,320
Do you want to hear a ghost story?

544
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:34,720
Thirty, right?

545
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,552
Correct.

546
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:40,720
Here.

547
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:41,920
Alright.

548
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:48,840
Then have a taste.

549
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,080
It's really tasty.

550
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:51,120
Tell me the ghost story.

551
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,720
Oh, there is no ghost story.

552
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,080
It was just a joke!

553
00:24:56,736 --> 00:24:57,320
Hey,

554
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,480
how can you do that?

555
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,720
You said you won't scam people.

556
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:00,840
Well...

557
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:03,120
Listen to me.

558
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,840
Look over there.

559
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,440
Isn't it very scary?

560
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:12,720
Is she jumping into the sea?

561
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:26,960
Hello?

562
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:31,320
Yu Lan?

563
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:36,960
Where's Li Yanhao?

564
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,080
He went out

565
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:39,440
and said something about walking

566
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,840
after meals for living long.

567
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:41,840
What?

568
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,480
I think you can find him by the seaside.

569
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,080
Li Yanhao!

570
00:25:47,600 --> 00:25:48,960
He dared to leave me alone again!

571
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,960
You're dead meat!

572
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:56,080
I'm not about jumping into the sea.

573
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:57,600
I just want to stand alone for a bit.

574
00:25:58,800 --> 00:25:59,360
But you

575
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:01,080
stand on such a dark coast alone.

576
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:03,040
What's anyone supposed to think?

577
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,080
I need some time to think.

578
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:10,600
I messed the meeting up this afternoon.

579
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:12,960
Did your senior give you a hard time?

